{% from "govuk/components/warning-text/macro.njk" import govukWarningText %}

<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Barcode expired: carry out further checks</h1>
<p data-qa="created-date">
  This barcode was created <strong>{{ form.errorCode.createdDate | calculateDaysSinceCreation }} days ago, on {{ form.errorCode.createdDate | formatDate('D MMMM YYYY') }}</strong>.
</p>
<p>
  Because this item of mail took longer than {{ form.errorCode.barcodeExpiryDays }} days to arrive you need to investigate further.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">How to investigate</h2>
<p>Follow your usual procedures, for example:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li data-qa="created-by">confirm the sender, <strong>{{ form.errorCode.createdBy }}</strong>, has a record of sending this item</li>
    <li>check the item has not been tampered with</li>
    <li>make sure there are no drugs or other contraband concealed in the item</li>
</ul>

<p>If you still have concerns, report them to a security manager.</p>
{{ govukWarningText({
  text: 'Do not open any item of Rule 39 mail without permission from a governor and the recipient being present.'
}) }}
